main event: A witness observed a round metallic object reflecting sunlight in Miami, Florida on January 25, 1965.
interesting points: The object was yellowish-red in color., The observation lasted for approximately 10 minutes., The witness was at the same altitude as the object at 16,000 ft., The case was marked as closed due to insufficient data., The witness was located in his backyard during a separate sighting on June 25, 1965.
witness description: The witness stated they observed the object hovering about 3 miles away.
